{
  "stem": "10818.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in fact, they left a rather large part of the old town standing, in order to protect the cathedral.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that is still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But much of the bombed-out parts are still being rebuilt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they are-- much of it is now pedestrian areas, so that the center of town is no longer accessible by cars.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's all around it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So then the-- then the newer part, where we lived, which was only settled in the 1800s, broad boulevards, pleasant streets, but mostly apartment-- low apartment houses.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There are a lot of private homes also in the areas that are a little more outlying, expensive areas.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Around between 2,000 and 3,000, in a-- in a town of a population of about 130,000.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, the-- the community was a very old one, which had periodically been destroyed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have a timeline in the museum there which showed that there were times when it dwindled down to almost nothing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Particularly in 1096, the time of the First Crusade, which had enormous repercussions and the community was almost wiped out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, when-- if you remember your Yom Kippur service, there is-- in-- in the-- in the Machzor, there is a-- a space of all the-- all the places where there were martyrs in the martyrology.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Mayence, which is the French name for Mainz, is one of them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Also, in the Yom Kippur service and in the-- in the Rosh Hashanah service, there is a very important prayer, the Unesanneh [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Tokef. ?] We called it [? 'tao-kef.' ?] It's Unesanneh Tokef, which was written by one of the martyrs in Mainz just before he died.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it has remained in-- in-- in the service ever since.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
